column1: Daily Weather Observations for Cranbourne, Victoria for March 2016
Prepared at 13:03 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW3019.201603
Most observations taken from Cranbourne, pressure taken from Moorabbin.
Moorabbin is several kilometres WNW of Cranbourne, so the pressures will sometimes be different.
Temperature, humidity, wind, cloud, evaporation and rainfall observations are from Cranbourne Botanic Gardens {station 086375}
Pressure observations are from Moorabbin Airport {station 086077}
